     <int-org-section id="PIF-SEC.IO.120" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
          <heading>Finance</heading>
          <p>The Governments of Australia and New Zealand each contribute 24.5% of the Forum Secretariat’s annual budget. The remaining amount is shared by the other member Governments. Extrabudgetary funding is contributed mainly by the EU, Australia, New Zealand, China and Japan.</p>
